{"tid":1140673,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果另一半分離焦慮我可以點做？","createTime":"2019-05-06T04:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T16:39:57.000Z","uid":182193,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d7e2335b40ae203291123a0ad76c79e6468a5bc2","tid":1140673,"uid":182193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T04:08:39.000Z","msg":"話說我同佢已經就嚟年半<br />\n佢係一個好缺乏安全感嘅人<br />\n要我匯報去咗邊其實我冇乜問題<br />\n但有時有啲活動overrun左佢就會好容易發脾氣<br />\n話我打破左啲承諾 明明話幾點幾點會完<br />\n之後如果我冇好好咁氹番佢<br />\n基本上會嬲好耐<br />\n重點係 有啲時間佢試過凌晨打嚟 又試過朝早打嚟<br />\n因為我不嬲都會覺月亮模式<br />\n(本身個人好易醒又會訓唔番)<br />\n所以有時真係好難先聽到電話<br />\n當第二日先發現佢打過嚟<br />\n佢好容易就會落入我唔重視佢<br />\n怪責我點解嗰一刻支持唔到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我平時佢有乜嘢事我都唔會衝過去<br />\n大小事佢佢會嫌麻煩我都盡量幫佢做<br />\n佢而家又講分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實明明大家都好愛大家<br />\n我唔明點解成日都要互相批評咁款<br />\n可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b44f6e621133fed158a22c6ac5c06d07734765","tid":1140673,"uid":126100,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T04:17:34.000Z","msg":"精神病，飛"},{"pid":"456fb12734411832c8dd1cdce0c1ea17a0643645","tid":1140673,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T04:18:03.000Z","msg":"樓主遲早有焦慮症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d01cdc2b44b90bead60f13f25aab9ddcf6c598","tid":1140673,"uid":21187,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T04:18:59.000Z","msg":"呢啲事，不論男女，到最後唔係你癲就佢癲"},{"pid":"dda1e577cf28d888abb76e84e4af9dc7178b8733","tid":1140673,"uid":19155,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:13:04.000Z","msg":"分<br />\n過黎人，你改變唔到佢，你就預咗要咁樣一世<br />\n<br />\n想改變佢<br />\n唔係唔得，難囉，要佢知道自己問題，肯改<br />\n<br />\n無安全感<br />\n公主病<br />\n唔體諒人<br />\nEq 低<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n你改得佢邊樣？"},{"pid":"3e1958cd898f0edc9ffca3a518fbf5fa7bef4c57","tid":1140673,"uid":182193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"456fb12734411832c8dd1cdce0c1ea17a0643645","tid":1140673,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T04:18:03.000Z","msg":"樓主遲早有焦慮症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:28:07.000Z","msg":"其實好多事情我已經好警戒，你對佢做好啲，但每一次都一鬆懈咗或者自己都有情緒困擾嘅時候，佢咁啱就係佢唔得嘅時候。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9998f6fd4846a84a2d8bfcf4570ff5ffda644bd","tid":1140673,"uid":90820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e1958cd898f0edc9ffca3a518fbf5fa7bef4c57","tid":1140673,"uid":182193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"456fb12734411832c8dd1cdce0c1ea17a0643645","tid":1140673,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T04:18:03.000Z","msg":"樓主遲早有焦慮症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:28:07.000Z","msg":"其實好多事情我已經好警戒，你對佢做好啲，但每一次都一鬆懈咗或者自己都有情緒困擾嘅時候，佢咁啱就係佢唔得嘅時候。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:34:09.000Z","msg":"好大壓力㗎<br />\n搵個社工或者心理學家拍拖就得<br />\n普通人真係頂唔順<br />\n遲早到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e87268ecfa3b9a323d6116b1ed0144ed1bd91f31","tid":1140673,"uid":182193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dda1e577cf28d888abb76e84e4af9dc7178b8733","tid":1140673,"uid":19155,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:13:04.000Z","msg":"分<br />\n過黎人，你改變唔到佢，你就預咗要咁樣一世<br />\n<br />\n想改變佢<br />\n唔係唔得，難囉，要佢知道自己問題，肯改<br />\n<br />\n無安全感<br />\n公主病<br />\n唔體諒人<br />\nEq 低<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n你改得佢邊樣？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:35:40.000Z","msg":"坦白講我係佢身上搵到好多優點，自己都好擅長係人身上搵優點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我好明白佢嘅需要，但有時我會覺得我真係唔可以隨時隨地就回應到佢情緒，我只係想如果當自己都好失控，自己處理返自己情緒再傾過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇安全感係延伸到好多唔同嘅嘢出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"042e0b352cb1295a3f7c46faff362003ef8f21dd","tid":1140673,"uid":182193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9998f6fd4846a84a2d8bfcf4570ff5ffda644bd","tid":1140673,"uid":90820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e1958cd898f0edc9ffca3a518fbf5fa7bef4c57","tid":1140673,"uid":182193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"456fb12734411832c8dd1cdce0c1ea17a0643645","tid":1140673,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T04:18:03.000Z","msg":"樓主遲早有焦慮症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:28:07.000Z","msg":"其實好多事情我已經好警戒，你對佢做好啲，但每一次都一鬆懈咗或者自己都有情緒困擾嘅時候，佢咁啱就係佢唔得嘅時候。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:34:09.000Z","msg":"好大壓力㗎<br />\n搵個社工或者心理學家拍拖就得<br />\n普通人真係頂唔順<br />\n遲早到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:36:49.000Z","msg":"其實我同佢都係社工學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a350049181272590fe11c4c9596c4d4748d4ce","tid":1140673,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"042e0b352cb1295a3f7c46faff362003ef8f21dd","tid":1140673,"uid":182193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9998f6fd4846a84a2d8bfcf4570ff5ffda644bd","tid":1140673,"uid":90820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e1958cd898f0edc9ffca3a518fbf5fa7bef4c57","tid":1140673,"uid":182193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:28:07.000Z","msg":"其實好多事情我已經好警戒，你對佢做好啲，但每一次都一鬆懈咗或者自己都有情緒困擾嘅時候，佢咁啱就係佢唔得嘅時候。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:34:09.000Z","msg":"好大壓力㗎<br />\n搵個社工或者心理學家拍拖就得<br />\n普通人真係頂唔順<br />\n遲早到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"re